Differents writing paterns,
UpperCamelCase  (ClassNames / ClassFilename.cpp/.hpp) - ClassFiles.hpp should be on class folder,
Uppercase letter on each Words,
lowerCamelCase (Functions),
Uppercase letter on each words except the 1st letter,
snake_case (Variables / other_filenames.cpp),
All lowercase, words separated by underscores,
_private_snake_case (Private variables),
All lowercase, words separated by underscores and starts with underscore